  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK723">
<l>pakaiyakattuc cāvā reḷiya rariya </l>
<l>ravaiyakat tañcā tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Many indeed may (fearlessly) die in the presence of (their) foes (but) few are those who are fearless in the assembly (of the learned).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
